NGCS Contracting Services, specialized handling small projects repairs, maintenance, remodeling and home improvements. ​ 

Providing professional Handyman services to keep your property well maintained, we have the experience, skills and special tools to perform the job professionally and accordingly. We strive hard to perform our services professionally and to accomplish our tasks on time. ​ 

Contact us today to obtain free estimate.
